Šimon Ornest: We want to accumulate positive energy at the concerts
What do you think about the end of the world in less than a month?
It&#39;s just one of the other alarmist messages we humans like to fall for.
Together with the band The Tap Tap, we rather joke about it and say that we are the only band in the world that can muster enough positive energy to delay or prevent the end of the world.
In December, you will also organize a completely unique project, three concerts against the end of the world.
Can you introduce him to the readers?
It is a national benefit event that we have been planning for two years.
We decided to take advantage of the marketing potential of the end of the Mayan calendar announced on December 21st at 11:10 am.
The day before, December 20, from 9 p.m., 3 concerts will take place simultaneously in Prague, Brno and Ostrava.
They will end around the time the Mayan calendar ends on the island of Kiribati in the Pacific, which is 12 hours ahead of us in the time zone.
Who came up with this idea?
