The server www.bankovnipoplatky.com, which annually announces a poll for the most absurd bank fee, has now decided to announce a competition for &quot;the most absurd regulation or ideas from the EU workshop&quot;.
&quot;We were led to this by the latest event, when the EU plans to adopt a 40 percent quota for women in the management of large European companies,&quot; survey organizer Patrik Nacher told Práv.
